Activities/Events:

Sports:
-Red Sox Game
--Fenway Park in the Fenway Neighborhood
--Oldest stadium in the MLB

-Celtics Game
--TD Garden in Downtown Boston
--The most successful basketball franchise in the NBA

-Bruins Game
--TD Garden in Downtown Boston
--Team that rostered the first black NHL player

-Ice skating
--Frog Pond in the Boston Commons (Oldest public park in the U.S.)
--Winter Wonderland in Government Center

-Kayaking
--Charles River 

-Boston Symphony Orchestra 
--Second oldest symphony of the 5 major American symphonies 
--Located in the Fenway neighborhood

-Theater Shows
--Go to a Broadway touring show in the Theater District
